*Kriv* je za sve što se dogodilo. (He is guilty for everything that happened.)

Ona je *kriva* zato što je izdala njegovu tajnu. (She is guilty because she revealed his secret.)

On je *krivac* za svoje greške. (He is guilty for his mistakes.)

Oni su *krivi* za uništavanje životne sredine. (They are guilty for destroying the environment.)

*Krive* su okolnosti zbog kojih je došlo do sukoba. (The circumstances are guilty for the conflict.)